Although the sample client app does use Kotlin, note that it does not use any androidx librar-
ies or other third-party libraries. This is intentional, because the app is built as part of the 
AOSP platform, which does not use Gradle. This means standard libraries available in Android 
Studio via Maven repositories are not readily available with the built-in Android app package 
rules when building via soong. Integrating Gradle into the AOSP build is possible, but it is out-
side of the scope of this book.
